2 Desert Butcher shop
2.1 Materials
2.2 Blueprint
The only difference between these wooden butcher shops is that the plains villages have oak wood, the taiga villages have spruce wood, and savanna villages have acacia wood.

Note: The oak wood stairs are optional and will only generate if the butcher shop was generated above street level. The back kennel area of the shop does indeed generate with dirt, but for villages inside plains biomes grass will soon spread over the area. The butcher shop sometimes generates horizontally flipped to the diagrams below.
